NO_CI_CHECK_IN_COMMENT

public static final java.lang.String NO_CI_CHECK_IN_COMMENT
The comment String which signals the continuous integration system to ignore a check-in. Any check-in with this String at any point in the comment will be ignored (i.e. will not trigger a new build).

See Also:
Constant Field Values
Constant Field Value:
"***NO_CI***"
